data.description: Sitting on a corner lot is your totally renovated ranch style home. The long driveway leads you into the side door, which opens into the mud room. Or walk onto your covered front porch and step inside to see the open floor plan with recessed lights, LVP flooring and renovations throughout the house. Your kitchen has marble countertops, blue base cabinets and stainless-steel appliances. Both full bathrooms have dual vanities and blue upgraded countertops. Schools, shopping and entertainment are nearby.
